settings.helpText: Optional. An URL to be linked by the "Read more" button. The button won't be shown if this URL is not provided.
Optional. Announcement type to show as a tag on the announcement.
Optional. The date/time after which the announcement will be shown. If not specified, the announcement will be shown always before the end date
Optional. The date after which the announcement should not be shown. If not provided, it may be shown any date after the start.
Should be a proper color value or name, that is understood by CSS.

The title of Leaderboard. It is strongly recommended to use track name with upper case
